### user register
POST http://localhost:4000/users-api/users 
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "firstname":"ishu",
    "lastname":"chirra",
    "email":"ishu.author@example.com",
    "password":"author",
    "profileImageUrl":"http://exmaple.com/avatars/author.png"
}     

###  user login
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ 
    "email":"ishu.author@example.com",
    "password":"author"
    
}

### author register
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/users
